name: Groovy Skulls Passaport
description:
Welcome to the Groovy Skulls Cemetery!

You can purchase this NFT as a passport, guaranteeing a random Groovy Skulls that will be shipped within 2 days of burning this item.

All Groovys will now have 10% royalties for the artist.

We'll only have 499 more Groovys, enjoy.

Questions please get in touch via the official twitter or "discord" of the community.
